o-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104lcu1665702733190.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lcu1665702733190.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/lcu1665702733190.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"lcu1665702733190\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      upgrade packages\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Generate packages only with the Create Table utility, not tables and indexes.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__topic_d56120e1_d56121e1_d56122e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__p_d56123e1_d56124e1_d56125e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS = upgrade packages</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__p_d56126e1_d56127e1_d56128e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$ORA_PARAMS = up</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__section_fwr_gs4_jcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1158746e66\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__p_d56132e1_d56133e1_d56134e1\">If the connector option upgrade packages is set, the\n            Create Table utility generates only the <code class=\"ph codeph\">CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE</code> and\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY</code> statements, and not the\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">CREATE TABLE</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">CREATE INDEX</code> statements which are\n            normally generated. This option does not affect the behavior of Uniface when creating\n            tables, indexes and packages on the fly.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"lcu1665702733190__p_d56135e1_d56136e1_d56137e1\">The SQL script generated by the Create Table utility\n            when this option is set can only be executed on a schema if the associated tables\n            already exist in that schema. When you attempt to create the packages in a schema where\n            the associated tables do not yet exist, obscure PL/SQL compilation errors occur.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ygq1665702777908.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Oracle Stored Packages</a><p>Uniface generates stored packages containing procedures for most basic I/O operations.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mel1665702961174.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Upgrade Stored Packages</a></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529505\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529505\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "upgrade packages Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 upgrade packages Generate packages only with the Create Table utility, not tables and indexes. USYS$ORA_PARAMS = upgrade packages USYS$ORA_PARAMS = up Description If the connector option upgrade packages is set, the Create Table utility generates only the CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE and CREATE OR REPLACE PACKAGE BODY statements, and not the CREATE TABLE and CREATE INDEX statements which are normally generated. This option does not affect the behavior of Uniface when creating tables, indexes and packages on the fly. The SQL script generated by the Create Table utility when this option is set can only be executed on a schema if the associated tables already exist in that schema. When you attempt to create the packages in a schema where the associated tables do not yet exist, obscure PL/SQL compilation errors occur. Related Links Oracle Stored Packages Uniface generates stored packages containing procedures for most basic I/O operations. Upgrade Stored Packages Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}